  </svg>GaN-Powered Efficiency</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">By using GaN (Gallium Nitride) components in our charging circuits, we reduce the footprint and improve thermal dissipation in our 2-in-1 Hybrid Chargers.</p>
                        </div>
